modName: AZ Argonian Khajiit Vampire No Color Change
summary: Argonians and Khajiit no longer change color on becoming a vampire.
descriptionHtml:
Argonians and Khajiit no longer change color on becoming a vampire.

This Mod has no effect if your character is already a vampire.

Place as close as possible to last in your Load Order.
author: AurinZalas
